factory.test.mock

Class EventLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • factory.test.mock.EventLog

  • public class EventLog
extends java.lang.Object
    This class should be used by Mock agents to log significant events. For example, you might write a log entry every time a Mock receives a message. The class exposes some helper methods to allow you to easily parse and search these log files.
    Author:
    Sean Turner
